
Di tmura n [[Itargiyen|yitargiyen]] '''amnukal''' (asget ''Imenukalen'') neɣ tamnukalt ma d tameṭṭut ( asget timnukalin ) , d aɣella n tgelda tatergit , yettwafran seg yimawlan n umnukal i t-id-yezwaren . Ttaken-as daɣen aɣara n aṭbel ( ṭṭbel n ṭṭrad ) am ucraḍ i uglad-is .. Awal-agi yezmer ad yemmel " amenkad " . Amnukal atergi yettwasnen aṭas d tagellidt [[Tin hinan]] , imi d tamezzwarut i wumi yettunefka uɣara-agi .
